WEBVTT

00:00:00.500 --> 00:00:02.000
The Web is always changing.

00:00:02.500 --> 00:00:04.300
And the way we access it is changing.

00:00:04.600 --> 00:00:07.000
From desktop computers to mobile phones,

00:00:07.200 --> 00:00:09.500
and now to smart devices and voice assistants.

00:00:09.800 --> 00:00:12.200
Every shift brings new opportunities,

00:00:12.400 --> 00:00:14.700
but also new challenges for developers and users alike.

00:00:15.000 --> 00:00:17.800
Web standards evolve to make experiences faster,

00:00:18.000 --> 00:00:20.200
more secure, and more accessible to everyone.

00:00:20.500 --> 00:00:23.000
As the Internet continues to grow,

00:00:23.200 --> 00:00:25.700
our goal remains the same:

00:00:25.900 --> 00:00:28.000
to keep the Web open and available to all.
